item.title: CVE-2021-3577|2024-08-03T17:01:07.325Z -- motorola -- binatone%20hubble%20cameras
item.description: An unauthenticated remote code execution vulnerability was reported in some Motorola-branded Binatone Hubble Cameras that could allow an attacker on the same network unauthorized access to the device.
